# Or bionic
FROM ubuntu:bionic
LABEL author="Bumsik Kim <k.bumsik@gmail.com>"

RUN apt-get update && \
    apt-get install --no-install-recommends -y python3-all python3-pip python3-wheel fakeroot debmake debhelper fakeroot wget tar curl && \
    apt-get autoremove -y && \
    ln /usr/bin/python3 /usr/bin/python && \
    ln /usr/bin/pip3 /usr/bin/pip && \
    rm -rf /var/cache/apt/archives/*.deb && \
    pip install --no-cache-dir virtualenv && \
    pip install --no-cache-dir --upgrade pip setuptools

# Get Miniconda and make it the main Python interpreter
RUN wget https://repo.continuum.io/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -O ~/miniconda.sh && \
    bash ~/miniconda.sh -b -p ~/miniconda && \
    rm ~/miniconda.sh

# AppImageKit
WORKDIR /opt
RUN wget https://github.com/AppImage/AppImageKit/releases/download/10/appimagetool-x86_64.AppImage && \
    chmod a+x appimagetool-x86_64.AppImage && \
    ./appimagetool-x86_64.AppImage --appimage-extract && \
    mv squashfs-root appimagetool && \
    rm appimagetool-x86_64.AppImage
ENV PATH=/opt/appimagetool/usr/bin:$PATH

WORKDIR /app
CMD ["/bin/bash"]
